---
// src/pages/design-system.astro
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import '../styles/global.css';

// Using Space Grotesk for data, Newsreader for editorial, Inter for body
---

<BaseLayout title="Formal Design Reference | Lupine">
  <main class="reference-container">
    <header class="formal-header">
      <div class="seal">VALIDATED // NIST-884 COMPLIANT</div>
      <h1>Lupine Design Reference</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">Institutional Validation & Formal Layout Primitives</p>
    </header>

    <section class="reading-layout">
      <div class="marginalia">
        <span class="citation-note">[1] Stillinger, F. H., & Weber, T. A. (1985). Computer simulation of local order in condensed phases of silicon. <em>Physical Review B</em>.</span>
        <span class="citation-note">[2] Daw, M. S., & Baskes, M. I. (1984). Embedded-atom method. <em>Physical Review B</em>.</span>
      </div>
      <article class="manuscript">
        <h2>1. Formal Research Brief</h2>
        <p>This layout primitive serves as the foundation for heavy technical documentation, Lean 4 specifications, and peer-reviewed methodological briefs. It employs a strict typographic hierarchy using <em>Newsreader</em> for editorial weight, juxtaposed against marginalia structured for deep-dive annotations without disrupting the primary narrative.</p>
        
        <div class="equation-block">
          <span class="math-label">Eq. 1.1 — Empirical Potential Energy</span>
          <div class="math-body">
            {String.raw`V(r^N) = \sum_{i<j} v_2(r_{ij}) + \sum_{i<j<k} v_3(r_{ij}, r_{ik}, \theta_{ijk})`}
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <p>The structure above ensures maximum legibility and communicates extreme confidence and academic rigor, allowing the physical equations to breathe within their own dedicated, sharply-defined blocks.</p>
      </article>
    </section>

    <section class="validation-table-container">
      <h2>2. Institutional Validation Manuscript</h2>
      <p class="summary-text">Validation Protocol (NIST-884 Compliance). Zero heavy borders; tabular figures ensure flawless vertical alignment.</p>
      <table class="validation-table">
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th>PARAMETER</th>
            <th>REFERENCE VAL.</th>
            <th>OBSERVED VAL.</th>
            <th>DELTA (Δ)</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr>
            <td>Lattice Constant (a)</td>
            <td class="data">5.4309 Å</td>
            <td class="data">5.4312 Å</td>
            <td class="data highlight-good">+0.0003</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Enthalpy of Formation</td>
            <td class="data">-4.63 eV/atom</td>
            <td class="data">-4.61 eV/atom</td>
            <td class="data highlight-warn">+0.02</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Elastic Modulus (B)</td>
            <td class="data">97.6 GPa</td>
            <td class="data">97.8 GPa</td>
            <td class="data highlight-good">+0.2</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Isotropic Strain</td>
            <td class="data">0.0012</td>
            <td class="data">0.0014</td>
            <td class="data highlight-warn">+0.0002</td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </section>

    <section class="timeline-container">
      <h2>3. Protocol Compiler Timeline</h2>
      <div class="workflow-active">
        <span class="status-dot"></span> ACTIVE SYNTHESIS
      </div>
      
      <div class="timeline-nodes">
        <div class="node">
          <span class="node-title">NIST Ingestion (675+ potentials)</span>
          <div class="progress-bar"><div class="progress-fill" style="width: 84%"></div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="connector topographic-line"></div>
        <div class="node">
          <span class="node-title">Lattice Optimization</span>
          <span class="node-icon">⌬</span>
        </div>
        <div class="connector topographic-line"></div>
        <div class="node">
          <span class="node-title">Energy Descriptors</span>
          <span class="node-icon">⚛</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="logbook-terminal">
        <div class="log-header">COMPILER_LOGBOOK_V1.0.4</div>
        <div class="log-content">
          <div>[INIT] SYSTEM_SCAN_START</div>
          <div>[OK] NIST-884_MAPPING_COMPLETE</div>
          <div>[WAIT] LATTICE_HARDENING...</div>
          <div>[WARN] SIMPSON'S PARADOX DETECTED IN MEAM-AL ALLOY SET</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  /* Local Component Styles building on global.css */
  .reference-container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: var(--space-2xl) var(--space-xl);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-3xl);
  }

  .formal-header {
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--outline-variant);
    padding-bottom: var(--space-lg);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .seal {
    font-family: 'Space Grotesk', monospace;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    color: var(--primary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .formal-header h1 {
    font-family: 'Newsreader', serif;
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4rem);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.1;
    color: var(--on-surface);
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-xs);
  }

  .subtitle {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    color: var(--on-surface-variant);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  /* Formal Research Brief */
  .reading-layout {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 250px 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-2xl);
    align-items: start;
  }

  .marginalia {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-md);
    padding-top: var(--space-xl);
    position: sticky;
    top: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .citation-note {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--on-surface-variant);
    line-height: 1.5;
    border-left: 2px solid var(--primary-container);
    padding-left: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .manuscript h2 {
    font-family: 'Newsreader', serif;
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--on-surface);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .manuscript p {
    font-family: 'Newsreader', serif;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--on-surface);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
    max-width: 65ch;
  }

  .equation-block {
    background: var(--surface-container-low);
    padding: var(--space-xl);
    margin: var(--space-xl) 0;
    position: relative;
    max-width: 65ch;
  }

  .math-label {
    position: absolute;
    top: var(--space-sm);
    left: var(--space-sm);
    font-family: 'Space Grotesk', monospace;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--on-surface-variant);
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .math-body {
    font-family: 'Newsreader', serif;
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--on-surface);
    margin-top: var(--space-md);
  }

  /* Validation Table */
  .validation-table-container {
    max-width: 900px;
  }

  .validation-table-container h2 {
    font-family: 'Newsreader', serif;
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
  }

  .summary-text {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    color: var(--on-surface-variant);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
    font-size: 1rem;
  }

  .validation-table {
    width: 100%;
    border-collapse: collapse;
    text-align: left;
  }

  .validation-table th {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    color: var(--on-surface-variant);
    padding: var(--space-md) var(--space-sm);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--outline-variant);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .validation-table td {
    padding: var(--space-md) var(--space-sm);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--outline-variant);
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    color: var(--on-surface);
  }

  .validation-table td.data {
    font-family: 'Space Grotesk', monospace;
    font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;
  }

  .highlight-good {
    color: var(--secondary);
  }
  
  .highlight-warn {
    color: var(--tertiary);
  }

  /* Timeline Workflow */
  .timeline-container {
    background: var(--surface-container-low);
    padding: var(--space-2xl);
    max-width: 800px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    margin-top: var(--space-2xl);
  }

  .timeline-container h2 {
    font-family: 'Newsreader', serif;
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .workflow-active {
    font-family: 'Space Grotesk', monospace;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--primary);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .status-dot {
    width: 8px;
    height: 8px;
    background: var(--primary);
    border-radius: 50%;
    animation: pulse 2s infinite;
  }

  @keyframes pulse {
    0% { transform: scale(0.95); box-shadow: 0 0 0 0 rgba(71, 91, 156, 0.7); }
    70% { transform: scale(1); box-shadow: 0 0 0 6px rgba(71, 91, 156, 0); }
    100% { transform: scale(0.95); box-shadow: 0 0 0 0 rgba(71, 91, 156, 0); }
  }

  .timeline-nodes {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-md);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2xl);
  }

  .node {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    padding: var(--space-md);
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.03);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(44, 42, 40, 0.02);
  }

  .node-title {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .node-icon {
    font-family: 'Space Grotesk', monospace;
    color: var(--on-surface-variant);
    font-size: 1.2rem;
  }

  .progress-bar {
    width: 150px;
    height: 4px;
    background: var(--surface-container-high);
    border-radius: 2px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .progress-fill {
    height: 100%;
    background: var(--primary);
  }

  .connector {
    height: 30px;
    width: 2px;
    background: repeating-linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--outline-variant) 0, var(--outline-variant) 4px, transparent 4px, transparent 8px);
    margin-left: 20px;
  }

  .logbook-terminal {
    background: var(--on-surface);
    color: var(--surface);
    padding: var(--space-lg);
    font-family: 'Space Grotesk', monospace;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .log-header {
    color: var(--primary-fixed-dim);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
    padding-bottom: var(--space-sm);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
  }

  @media (max-width: 800px) {
    .reading-layout {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    .marginalia {
      position: static;
      flex-direction: row;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--outline-variant);
      padding-top: var(--space-md);
      margin-top: var(--space-md);
    }
    .validation-table {
      display: block;
      overflow-x: auto;
    }
  }
</style>
